red","page":587,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5833.mp3","colorText":"وَإِذَا [h:14357[ٱ]لْقُبُورُ بُعْثِرَتْ","juz":30,"ruku":524,"manzil":7,"htmlColorText":"وَإِذَا <span class=ham_wasl>ٱ</span>لْقُبُورُ بُعْثِرَتْ <span class=end>٤</span>"},{"id":5,"arabic_text":"عَلِمَتۡ نَفۡسٞ مَّا قَدَّمَتۡ وَأَخَّرَتۡ","bangl_text":"তখন প্রত্যেকে জেনে নিবে সে কি অগ্রে প্রেরণ করেছে এবং কি পশ্চাতে ছেড়ে এসেছে।","english_text":"A soul will [then] know what it has put forth and kept back","page":587,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5834.mp3","colorText":"عَلِمَتْ نَفْ[a:10644[سٌ م]َّا قَدَّمَتْ وَأَخَّرَتْ","juz":30,"ruku":524,"manzil":7,"htmlColorText":"عَلِمَتْ نَفْ<span class=idgham_ghunnah>سٌ م</span>َّا قَدَّمَتْ وَأَخَّرَتْ <span class=end>٥</span>"},{"id":6,"arabic_text":"يَـٰٓأَيُّهَا ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ مَا غَرَّكَ بِرَبِّكَ ٱلۡكَرِيمِ","bangl_text":"হে মানুষ, কিসে তোমাকে তোমার মহামহিম পালনকর্তা সম্পর্কে বিভ্রান্ত করল","english_text":"O mankind, what has deceived you concerning your Lord, the Generous","page":587,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5835.mp3","colorText":"يَ[o[ـٰٓ]أَيُّهَا [h:14358[ٱ]لْإِ[f:2732[نس]َ[n[ـٰ]نُ مَا غَرَّكَ بِرَبِّكَ [h:14359[ٱ]لْكَر[p[ِي]مِ","juz":30,"ruku":524,"manzil":7,"htmlColorText":"يَ<span class=madda_obligatory>ـٰٓ</span>أَيُّهَا <span class=ham_wasl>ٱ</span>لْإِ<span class=ikhafa>نس</span>َ<span class=madda_normal>ـٰ</span>نُ مَا غَرَّكَ بِرَبِّكَ <span class=ham_wasl>ٱ</span>لْكَر<span class=madda_permissible>ِي</span>مِ <span class=end>٦</span>"},{"id":7,"arabic_text":"ٱلَّذِي خَلَقَكَ فَسَوَّىٰكَ فَعَدَلَكَ","bangl_text":"যিনি তোমাকে সৃষ্টি করেছেন, অতঃপর তোমাকে সুবিন্যস্ত করেছেন এবং সুষম করেছেন।","english_text":"Who created you, proportioned you, and balanced you","page":587,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5836.mp3","colorText":"ٱلَّذِى خَلَقَكَ فَسَوَّ[n[ٮٰ]كَ فَعَدَلَكَ","juz":30,"ruku":524,"manzil":7,"htmlColorText":"ٱلَّذِى خَلَقَكَ فَسَوَّ<span class=madda_normal>ٮٰ</span>كَ فَعَدَلَكَ <span class=end>٧</span>"},{"id":8,"arabic_text":"فِيٓ أَيِّ صُورَةٖ مَّا شَآءَ رَكَّبَكَ","bangl_text":"যিনি তোমাকে তাঁর ইচ্ছামত আকৃতিতে গঠন করেছেন।","english_text":"In whatever form He willed has He assembled you","page":587,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5837.mp3","colorText":"ف[o[ِىٓ] أَىِّ صُورَ[a:14360[ةٍ م]َّا ش[o[َا]ٓءَ رَكَّبَكَ","juz":30,"ruku":524,"manzil":7,"htmlColorText":"ف<span class=madda_obligatory>ِىٓ</span> أَىِّ صُورَ<span class=idgham_ghunnah>ةٍ م</span>َّا ش<span class=madda_obligatory>َا</span>ٓءَ رَكَّبَكَ <span class=end>٨</span>"},{"id":9,"arabic_text":"كَلَّا بَلۡ تُكَذِّبُونَ بِٱلدِّينِ","bangl_text":"কখনও বিভ্রান্ত হয়ো না; বরং তোমরা দান-প্রতিদানকে মিথ্যা মনে কর।","english_text":"No! But you deny the Recompense","page":587,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5838.mp3","colorText":"كَلَّا بَلْ تُكَذِّبُونَ بِ[h:14361[ٱ][l[ل]دّ[p[ِي]نِ","juz":30,"ruku":524,"manzil":7,"htmlColorText":"كَلَّا بَلْ تُكَذِّبُونَ بِ<span class=ham_wasl>ٱ</span><span class=laam_shamsiyah>ل</span>دّ<span class=madda_permissible>ِي</span>نِ <span class=end>٩</span>"},{"id":10,"arabic_text":"وَإِنَّ عَلَيۡكُمۡ لَحَٰفِظِينَ","bangl_text":"অবশ্যই তোমাদের উপর তত্ত্বাবধায়ক নিযুক্ত আছে।","english_text":"And indeed, [appointed] over you are keepers","page":587,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5839.mp3","colorText":"وَإِ[g[نّ]َ عَلَيْكُمْ لَحَ[n[ـٰ]فِظ[p[ِي]نَ","juz":30,"ruku":524,"manzil":7,"htmlColorText":"وَإِ<span class=ghunnah>نّ</span>َ عَلَيْكُمْ لَحَ<span class=madda_normal>ـٰ</span>فِظ<span class=madda_permissible>ِي</span>نَ <span class=end>١٠</span>"},{"id":11,"arabic_text":"كِرَامٗا كَٰتِبِينَ","bangl_text":"সম্মানিত আমল লেখকবৃন্